## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="077cc-117">当<xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeBuffer.AcquirePointer%2A>返回时，应执行边界检查只需验证`pointer`参数是`null`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="077cc-117">When <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeBuffer.AcquirePointer%2A> returns, you should perform bounds checking by verifying that the `pointer` parameter is `null`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="077cc-118">如果不是`null`，必须调用<xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeBuffer.ReleasePointer%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>受约束的执行区域 (CER) 中的方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="077cc-118">If it is not `null`, you must call the <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeBuffer.ReleasePointer%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method in a constrained execution region (CER).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="077cc-119"><xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeBuffer.AcquirePointer%2A> 调用<xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeHandle.DangerousAddRef%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>方法，并公开指针。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="077cc-119"><xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeBuffer.AcquirePointer%2A> calls the <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeHandle.DangerousAddRef%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method and exposes the pointer.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="077cc-120">与不同<xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeBuffer.Read%2A>方法，它不会更改指针的当前位置。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="077cc-120">Unlike the <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeBuffer.Read%2A> method, it does not change the current position of the pointer.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="077cc-121">以下 exampledemonstrates 如何使用<xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeBuffer.AcquirePointer%2A>方法：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="077cc-121">The following exampledemonstrates how to use the <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeBuffer.AcquirePointer%2A> method:</span></span>  
  
```  
byte* pointer = null;  
RuntimeHelpers.PrepareConstrainedRegions();  
try {  
    MySafeBuffer.AcquirePointer(ref pointer);  
    // Use pointer here, with your own bounds checking.  
    }  
finally {  
    if (pointer != null)  
        MySafeBuffer.ReleasePointer();  
    }  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="077cc-122">如果将转换为`pointer`（这是指向一个字节的指针） 为指向不同的类型 （T \*） 的链接，则可能会产生指针对齐问题。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="077cc-122">If you cast `pointer` (which is a pointer to a byte) as a pointer to a different type (T\*), you may have pointer alignment issues.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="077cc-123">您必须负责所有的边界检查与此指针。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="077cc-123">You must take responsibility for all bounds checking with this pointer.</span></span>

